# SECTION 4: NAMING RULES

All names must use MemoSpark domain language. Generic names are rejected without exception.

## Variables

- data → streakRecord, scheduleEntries, moodLog
- result → updatedStreak, fetchedTimetable, savedCrashout
- item / items → courseSlot, streakDay, journalEntry, coinTx
- user → student (MemoSpark users are students)
