# SECTION 6: EMPTY STATES

**BANNED:** "No data available." / "No items found." / "Nothing here yet." / "No results." / "This list is empty."

**REQUIRED by feature:**

- No courses: "Add your first course and Stu will help you build a study plan around it."
- No streak: "Start your first study session today — your streak begins with one day."
- Broken streak: "Streaks break sometimes. Today is a fresh start."
- No crashout entries: "No mood entries yet. How are you feeling today?"
- No achievements: "Your first achievement is closer than you think — keep showing up."
- No social messages: "No conversations yet. Connect with a classmate to get started."
- No community posts: "Nothing posted yet. Be the first to share."
- No Stu suggestions: "Add your courses and Stu will start suggesting study sessions for you."
- No voice notes: "Nothing recorded yet. Tap the mic to add a voice note."
- Search empty: "No results for '[query]' — try different words or check the spelling."

