# SECTION 7: LOADING STATES

**BANNED:** `<Spinner />` alone; "Loading..." as standalone text; pulse over empty div; full-page spinner with no label.

**REQUIRED:** Skeleton loaders matching the exact shape of the real content. Three skeleton items visible while loading.

Loading copy by feature:

- Timetable: "Fetching your schedule..."
- Streaks: "Getting your streak..."
- Crashout: "Loading your mood log..."
- Stu: "Stu is thinking..."
- Social: "Loading your conversations..."
- Achievements: "Loading your achievements..."

For Stu specifically: animated typing indicator with name visible. "Stu is thinking..." with three animated dots. Never just a spinner.

